
### Get all shopping lists
GET {{url}}/shopping-lists
Authorization: Bearer {{authTokenHeadChef}}}

### Get by status DRAFT
GET {{url}}/shopping-lists?status=DRAFT
Authorization: Bearer {{authTokenHeadChef}}}

### Get by status FINALIZED
GET {{url}}/shopping-lists?status=FINALIZED
Authorization: Bearer {{authTokenHeadChef}}}

### Get by delivery date
GET {{url}}/shopping-lists?deliveryDate=2026-03-20
Authorization: Bearer {{authTokenHeadChef}}}

### Get by status and delivery date
GET {{url}}/shopping-lists?status=DRAFT&deliveryDate=2026-03-20
Authorization: Bearer {{authTokenHeadChef}}}

### Get shopping list by id
GET {{url}}/shopping-lists/1
Authorization: Bearer {{authTokenHeadChef}}}

### Generate shopping list from approved requests
POST {{url}}/shopping-lists
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authTokenHeadChef}}}

{
    "deliveryDate": "2026-03-20",
    "targetLanguage": "DA"
}

### Update delivery date
PATCH {{url}}/shopping-lists/1/delivery-date
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authTokenHeadChef}}}

{
    "deliveryDate": "2026-03-25"
}

### Add item manually
POST {{url}}/shopping-lists/1/items
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authTokenHeadChef}}}

{
    "ingredientName": "Smør",
    "quantity": 5.0,
    "unit": "KG",
    "supplier": "Arla"
}

### Update item
PUT {{url}}/shopping-lists/1/items/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authTokenHeadChef}}}

{
    "quantity": 10.0,
    "unit": "KG",
    "supplier": "Lurpak"
}

### Mark single item as ordered
PATCH {{url}}/shopping-lists/1/items/1/ordered
Authorization: Bearer {{authTokenHeadChef}}}

### Mark all items as ordered
PATCH {{url}}/shopping-lists/1/items/ordered
Authorization: Bearer {{authTokenHeadChef}}}

### Remove item
DELETE {{url}}/shopping-lists/1/items/1
Authorization: Bearer {{authTokenHeadChef}}}

### Finalize shopping list
POST {{url}}/shopping-lists/1/finalize
Authorization: Bearer {{authTokenHeadChef}}}

### Delete shopping list
DELETE {{url}}/shopping-lists/1
Authorization: Bearer {{authTokenHeadChef}}}

###
